{
  "stem": "7455.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "His inst-- intestines were ulcerated and dried up, like crumpled into pieces.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He recuperated at my aunt [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Anne's ?] and uncle's house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "He gained weight and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I went to the train to pick him up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "My mother said, he looks 20 years younger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He was rejuvenated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And for that, I always thought because of that miracle that week, our father came back to us, that God will spare us from future tragedy.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I was one of five children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "My oldest sister, Laura, six years older.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "My brother [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Munio ?] was two years older.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "He survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Then came my other half, my twin brother, older by another-- by half an hour, and my sister, Rosa.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Because we had a house and tenants and children-- they had children-- we had a built-in playmates.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "We did not have to play in the streets because it was like a small oasis.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "We had a garden.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "We played hide and seek, and all games, and hopscotch, and swinging, all the things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And life was good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "I, being born in Poland, speaking the language, educated in Poland-- this was my country.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "I didn't know any other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "I loved Poland until the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "We had a-- a substantial class of intellectuals-- doctors, lawyers, teachers, pharmacists.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "They had-- there was a middle class by American standards.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "They lived graciously.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "They had nice homes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "There was also a poor class because Brody was not an industrial city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And so they couldn't get steady jobs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "But the people had dignity as long as the daily requirements were met.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "They were grateful to God.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "There were also organizations, committees, charitable organizations that helped them discreetly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "[PAUSES] My sister Laura was very idealistic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "She joined a Zionist organization when-- before the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
